cht; er informiert dabei zuverlässig über die Fakten und führt in die umfangreiche Spezialliteratur ein.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aChurch and statezGermanyxHistoryy17th century. 0aChurch and statezGermanyxHistoryy18th century. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History 1990 - 1999z9783110635867oZDB-23-GHI0 cprintz978348655793040uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978348670217040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486702170423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486702170/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GHIc1990d1999